Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.97,0:02:00.41,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)\fs55}光を　もっと光を
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.52,0:02:02.82,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)\fs55}光を　もっと光を
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.82,0:02:06.75,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)}その頂きへと
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.93,0:02:09.49,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)}Have an obsession for victory
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.49,0:02:11.98,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)}I'm proud of myself and you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.04,0:02:14.71,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)}We must be the change we wish to see...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.32,0:01:14.30,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)}在囚笼中是绝对安全的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.30,0:01:19.49,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)}但忘却了创造的地方不会有光明
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.53,0:01:21.98,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)}诉说希望 驱散不满
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.98,0:01:23.87,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)}革命的信号
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.00,0:01:28.43,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)}突破到无人能及的境界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.43,0:01:34.38,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)}总有一天要超越修罗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.38,0:01:39.97,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)}就算现在压倒性的支配让我极度干渴
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.97,0:01:44.48,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)}只有梦不会被夺走
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.59,0:01:47.39,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)}燃烧吧 全部神经的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.45,0:01:52.16,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)}不知谁能收到的声音里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.16,0:01:57.49,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(70,70)}不会有意义
